{"tid":1342560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"未來警務處長，現任行動處副處長鄧炳強與元朗社團關係","createTime":"2019-07-21T17:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T16:07:42.000Z","uid":256019,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"118297be4ac75b590345ba983472bb3b3a5bf5da","tid":1342560,"uid":256019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:42:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kowloonsingjai/photos/a.644812365601137/2404043156344707/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkowloonsingjai%2Fphotos%2Fa.644812365601137%2F2404043156344707%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=Px13HBr2%2FanjjqouUL7W1C8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=e493473c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kowloonsingjai/photos/a.644812365601137/2404043156344707/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n行動處副處長鄧炳強是現時對付示威者的最高負責人，製訂沸水政策在旺角丶上水及沙田圍捕示威者，造成大規模衝突。<br />\n<br />\n大家可能唔記得，他在梁振英上場後，2012年出任元朗警區指揮官，同當地社團黑幫稔熟，離任時梁志祥丶錦田鄧賀年歡送。元朗黑幫一直是梁振英支持者，當日在朗晴村諮詢會曾樹和及一班流氓便公然為梁保駕護航。<br />\n<br />\n今日元朗黑幫公然在車廂襲擊市民，昨天消息已經廣泛流傳，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>今晚八點白衫流氓通街行，區議員丶居民報警冇人理，元朗警方絕對知情，他們是配合黑幫襲擊恫嚇香港人。我們有理由懷疑，究竟曾任元朗指揮官的行動處處長是否就是主謀？</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/22/LlTogb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F22%2FLlTogb.jpg&h=c0611b6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"549dd33a4dbd9fbb58ed9c710f4f6163efbcd2d1","tid":1342560,"uid":172633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"118297be4ac75b590345ba983472bb3b3a5bf5da","tid":1342560,"uid":256019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:42:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kowloonsingjai/photos/a.644812365601137/2404043156344707/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkowloonsingjai%2Fphotos%2Fa.644812365601137%2F2404043156344707%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=Px13HBr2%2FanjjqouUL7W1C8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=e493473c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kowloonsingjai/photos/a.644812365601137/2404043156344707/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n行動處副處長鄧炳強是現時對付示威者的最高負責人，製訂沸水政策在旺角丶上水及沙田圍捕示威者，造成大規模衝突。<br />\n<br />\n大家可能唔記得，他在梁振英上場後，2012年出任元朗警區指揮官，同當地社團黑幫稔熟，離任時梁志祥丶錦田鄧賀年歡送。元朗黑幫一直是梁振英支持者，當日在朗晴村諮詢會曾樹和及一班流氓便公然為梁保駕護航。<br />\n<br />\n今日元朗黑幫公然在車廂襲擊市民，昨天消息已經廣泛流傳，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>今晚八點白衫流氓通街行，區議員丶居民報警冇人理，元朗警方絕對知情，他們是配合黑幫襲擊恫嚇香港人。我們有理由懷疑，究竟曾任元朗指揮官的行動處處長是否就是主謀？</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/22/LlTogb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F22%2FLlTogb.jpg&h=c0611b6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:30:35.000Z","msg":"警黑合作將會進入新紀元<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf084264c6f055c41ff3c348f43f4e6503f902fb","tid":1342560,"uid":285858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:32:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07a4745b3723d1e0d6799a5188562f8afe98fa2c","tid":1342560,"uid":88817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:57:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"043da23d43f264b64627487d0d11d9b4851e1f4f","tid":1342560,"uid":279357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:05:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[gold保護義士<br />\n保護香港市民<br />\n<br />\n政府的壓力，中共，商家，罷工罷市<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1351563\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1351563</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區][/gold]</span>"},{"pid":"526534ee28fe4563ba41244bd3b7dd2c792ecd55","tid":1342560,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:07:42.000Z","msg":"推，一